{
  "texts": [
    "The weights of the models are sourced from Hug-gingFace (Wolf et al., 2020b).",
    "In addition, we opted for the 7B model size due to its ability to strike a favorable balance between performance and latency, especially when deployed in production contexts with 4-bit quantization.",
    "We adopt quantization methods that support finetuning LoRA adapters added to a quantized and freezed base model (i.e.",
    "QLoRA (Dettmers et al., 2023)) as of June 2024, which are bitsandbytes (BNB) foot_3 and GPTQ (Frantar et al., 2023).",
    "We choose 4-bit quantization for all models."
  ]
}